Diogma glabrata megacauda
in 
Alexander 1949
: 196: comparison; 
Ishida 1955
: 76: distribution; 
Takahashi 1960
: 82: distribution, comparison, illustration; 
Alexander 1966
: 122: distribution, faunistic records; 
Sidorenko 1999
